      "asbval:note": "Paper does compare outputs under different parameter settings ('comparing to the original or standard settings'), but this is parameter sensitivity analysis, not reproducibility validation. The paper does not address validating that re-executed code produces equivalent results to a reference implementation or checking for computational environment regressions.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10_1371_journal_pcbi_1009105",
