      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Using five publicly available datasets, we demonstrated that changes in parameters such as the background set, differential metabolite selection methods, and pathway database used can result in profoundly different ORA results... we vary the inputs, each time comparing to the original or standard settings, thus demonstrating the effect of these choices on the output lists of significant pathways.",
      "asbval:note": "The paper systematically varies parameters and compares outcomes across conditions, directly matching the research question.",
