      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "ORA was performed following the addition of each compound to the DA list... To this end, DA compound lists of increasing length were constructed by adding compounds, from lowest t-test p-value to highest, one at a time... we investigated how the size of the background set affects ORA results... we simulated a reduction in the number of compounds identified in the experiment",
